summary: Rise of the Water Evil is a small ice cave dungeon with rising water allowing to reach next steps of the caves.
descriptionHtml:
Rise of the Water Evil is a small ice cave dungeon with rising water allowing to reach next steps of the caves.

You may find the cave entrance north of Winterhold near the SkyTemple Ruins.
Joined a picture of the Map marker for the cave entrance.
The recommended level to fight in the cave is 15-20.

This small mod was created to fit the theme of the \"Underwater Mod Jam\" started in the \"Skyrim Creation Kit\" group.
http://steamcommunity.com/groups/SkyrimCKPublic/announcements/detail/921226174667132756

All comments are welcome =)
author: Hellay
